➜古生物篇：海底鱼那么多，为什么偏偏就它成了人类祖先？
http://www.sohu.com/a/428942286_624188	25569
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201102/37507806ce674024bc1273ba1345016b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如无意外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时你蹲到脚麻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">右手刷手机，左手擦菊花</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201102/b779d94b558c4c618ffca9dacc794015.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">先不管空气味道如何</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">咱们先来问个香喷喷的问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你的手脚是怎么来的？？？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201102/c7cc1f9d65b34588822e5785c4a2d826.gif" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
