<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">这问题就涉及到人类祖宗了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人说是<strong>猿猴</strong>赐的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而看过第二期古生物的爱卿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">则会自信说出祖宗大名：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（美人）鱼！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不记得的可以重温一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201102/611f2b542972446daa9ef701388ea1da.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远古生物图鉴：大多数人都不知道，有种蚊子比你的头还大 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">究竟谁才是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第一只爬上陆地的天选之鱼呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它又是怎么拿到陆地居住证呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它为什么这么想不开呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">欢迎进入——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大型人类认祖归宗上香现场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201102/2821b6ec700141ff97573d8612274348.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201102/0facf6f06cc0427aac3b8f44ce1bdbde.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201102/ebdf47378b134a16a38cf4373c54f597.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个天选故事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">得从<strong>4.2亿</strong>年前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云南<strong>曲靖</strong>那片浅海说起——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这片万物之源</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼类终于迎来了霸主时代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">霸主之一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却有着一个90后非主流名字——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>梦幻鬼鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201102/905bd47aa90843bba49381254e3543a1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古鱼有四大类</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>无颌类、盾皮类、软骨鱼类</strong>和<strong>硬骨鱼类</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦幻鬼鱼是硬骨鱼类成员</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">硬骨鱼类又分为<strong>辐鳍鱼</strong>和<strong>肉鳍鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦幻鬼鱼则是目前<strong>最古老</strong>的肉鳍鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它本应该出现在几亿年后的<strong>泥盆纪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却带着刚进化出的<strong>颌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">提早出生在<strong>志留纪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这条<strong>鱼中王莽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">准备带领硬骨鱼勇夺顶级猎食者的职称</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201102/fca2f0255fba40538e3b3b592f64b6e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然梦幻鬼鱼是硬骨鱼类</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但此时它们和古鲨鱼一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>体内都是软骨，没有硬骨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这哪能在陆地上爬呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦幻鬼鱼是来冒认人类祖先的吧？！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201102/fb233d95a7594c79966a09b8091d612f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然硬骨鱼很软</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但它有个必杀技——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>鳔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当其他平民鱼扎在深海里埋头苦干时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">硬骨鱼还能用鱼鳔吸海面上的<strong>氧气</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼鳔还能让硬骨鱼游得更快</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有鳔游得快</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有颌猎食狠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">硬骨鱼类开始环球漂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开启<strong>鱼三桂</strong>殖民时代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拿下了曾经的海洋霸主——<strong>海蝎</strong>和<strong>盾皮鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摧毁无嵴椎动物的旧世界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开启嵴椎动物的霸权世界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201102/060dfdf2afe24d31b2b963224efbb46f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">偏偏肉鳍鱼就是打不过盾皮鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本应成为鱼类MVP的它却面临灭族抄家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201102/4ed434e4a87940108166b45096069eea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经过几千万年的演化</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肉鳍鱼团队终于有鱼咸鱼翻身——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>空棘鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201102/9e1309230ece4ddebcab3d627e447a4e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">空棘鱼的身体进化得<strong>四平八稳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能在夹缝中生存</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>它躲猫猫一级棒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>超级能苟，苟到现在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这货的老实body能保命</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却也断送了进化生涯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四亿年都长那个鱼样儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">堪称<strong>活化石中的活化石</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201102/bb7deb85586348a68d8737400bb2a31c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201102/439e7d82b90b4fd08cf6d3cefeea9417.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>珍·兹基硕德</strong>曾经说过</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
<strong>与其苟活，不如逃避</strong>
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其他看破海洋的肉鳍鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">准备离海出走</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遁入<strong>淡水</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">淡水里没有盾皮鱼的追杀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有软骨鱼和刺鱼这些食物链中低端的猎物作伴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201102/8fb61cc9c426413cb638abf0dcf2c483.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">慢着，问题一来了——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼儿眼神不太好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它看得清远方吗?</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水下昏暗的环境让鱼儿<strong>视觉退化</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即使水面阳光充足</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它的死鱼眼只是一副摆设</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">视力低相当于<strong>没有GPS带路</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眼科专家<strong>提塔利克鱼</strong>登场了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是开头那条吵着上岸打工的鸡掰鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201102/9bcabbdd1efd4680a76615117d909e37.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">适者生存</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡掰鱼的双眼尺寸增长到原来的<strong>3倍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这意味着瞳孔变大了，视力变好了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它的<strong>眼窝由两侧移到头部顶端</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肉鳍鱼只要一贴近水面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就能清楚看到陆地猎物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201102/c4278b10dfdb48c7b679d6f6a1fcc3bf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>——淡水终于迎来了顶级猎食者</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肉鳍鱼最爱围殴<strong>古鲨鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">处在古生物时代的食物链底层</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鲨鱼在海洋里被盾皮鱼<strong>追着打</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">躲到淡水里又被肉鳍鱼<strong>围着殴</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这才造就了当代鲨鱼钢铁般的意志</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">进地铁安检都能响起铜铃般的响声</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这要感谢那些曾经伤害它的鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201102/6730897e48ab46a693d0d6565271cd76.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201102/b24615b405424cce89858b30d9963441.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肉鳍鱼在淡水里的滋润日子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没一会儿就到头了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>泥盆纪后期</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陆地植物茂盛过头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">营养物质全跑到水里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">导致水里<strong>营养过剩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201102/ca19a6b2298a4387affb05ac4cf566aa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">藻类会把水里氧气榨干</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">造成缺氧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很多鱼都被淹死了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而肉鳍鱼继续发扬<strong>逃避不可耻</strong>的传统</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逃到岸上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201102/fda972b6eeb04b0896364045dac60af8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">幸好肉鳍鱼在几亿年前抽中了<strong>鱼鳔SSR卡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是能在岸上呼吸到一点点氧的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一点点早晚成为<strong>亿点点</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四足动物的<strong>肺</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是这样由鱼鳔进化来的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201102/823cc21744044a72bb02638dac852470.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">部份肉鳍鱼吸到的氧气不够用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是肉鳍鱼又衍生出了<strong>肺鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当水缺氧时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>肺鱼</strong>就进入<strong>死宅模式休眠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将身体代谢率降到最低</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一丢丢空气就能满足身体所需</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201102/208aac7ee7e7402ca65e57504b94d6c5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经过这么多年的肥宅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">非洲肺鱼能靠肺自主呼吸（还没有鼻孔）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成了世界上唯一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丢进水里会淹死的鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201102/8e94b35d497c4fd18e498e728d8d1f81.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201102/6b5bb918b930427b9871712146050a75.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">幸好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡掰鱼和<strong>潘氏鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正确解锁了鱼鳃的使用方法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不然鱼鳃就失传了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201102/eaab5d862ac4457094d6eb46d15195b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问题三又来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陆地没有交通工具</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只能靠鱼工11路车——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>爬！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不会爬的鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哪都去不了，登陆了也没用啊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>鸡掰鱼</strong>完美解锁了长辈<strong>周氏鸿鱼</strong>的鱼鳍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">学会了在河底爬行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">周氏的骨骼和肌肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比当时的嵴椎动物都<strong>硬了</strong>很多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让硬骨鱼从此不再软</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发达的骨头早就为登陆做好了准备</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201102/5ec4788c995c48949531ccba68812a38.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这里特别要提醒的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要转行成为一名合格的两栖动物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼鳍必须有<strong>鳍条</strong>和<strong>指骨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不然在陆地爬不起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那鸡掰鱼第一个就被踢出局了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为它没有指骨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只能在河底爬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201102/9794eec62fd54574bfbe503c259eb1f9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201102/c65e84c73c554da8a8dfca86af6a79ae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>鱼石螈</strong>和<strong>棘螈</strong>一直被称为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>第一条成为四足动物的鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但最近研究发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它有指骨但没有鳍条</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>无法完全脱离水环境</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201102/c6497d6e29ce4e198340093d9683ca66.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201102/1294d0f65aac47ab8fed7f5b40f9eb64.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不是所有肉鳍鱼最后都能爬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那条非洲肺鱼的鱼鳍就退化成了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一条须子！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201102/67e7de6de43840d38946a4cd8e626b59.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">究竟谁才是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拿到陆地居住证的第一鱼呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201102/97e3f297eb5f44138155ea060e002450.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020年3月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古生物学家公布了答案——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>希望螈</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就目前来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它比提塔利克鱼（鸡掰鱼）更接近四足动物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古生物学家还推测</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在进化过程中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当<strong>Hox基因</strong>突然缺失时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">胸鳍就一不小心演化成你刷手机和擦屁屁的双手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">腹鳍则成了你蹲坑的双脚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>基因缺失</strong>也能是福不是祸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肝作业肝到秃头也可能不是一件坏事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老师们请大力加作业吧！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201102/27a6442e345e4d34a9ddc93d58c18a6c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既然会爬，又会呼吸岸上空气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么登陆吧！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">希望螈！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但自古以来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">攻打别国总得师出有名</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它亮出的名头就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>本鱼吃腻了海底捞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我得吃吃陆底捞！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陆地努力进化的本地小生物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是被外省鱼打了个措手不及</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成了一桌又一桌盆菜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201102/0241d6f5da2e4ff48af8178dab366637.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">希望螈体验到了这种想吃啥吃啥的爽感</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它立志不做鱼了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从此海洋就是回不去的故乡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它办了陆地二代身份证</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（暂时）成了人类的祖宗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201102/d2410534debd48cb9331093ee580dd0f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201102/34dd5da0503941b5abaf33de61d025ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">希望螈只是暂代祖先</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为好景不长</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>物种大规模入侵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>泥盆纪生物灭绝了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">希望螈化石只是幸运被找到了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">未来会找到哪些更古老化石</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古生物学家还在<strong>暴躁等待中</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">登陆第一鱼还不能确认</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201102/3973e6cf61394b33bf6f78edfc180743.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>肉鳍鱼的祖先</strong>还是能确认的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">5.4亿年前的后口动物——<strong>冠状皱囊动物！！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（别怀疑！这货不是外星人！)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(它的大口正是肛门本门！)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你必须含泪承认</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后口动物再丑萌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它也是人类祖宗的祖宗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201102/d04794afa7af4c37a064eef371d72a11.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201102/5345ac43337a4e55afcb4b61e2f6329e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>综上所述</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>朕宣布</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>本次大型认祖宗仪式</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>暂告失败</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">祖坟暂时找不到了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱卿（可能）下次再会</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记得买香么么哒！！！</p>
